{"tid":252301,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友想減肥 有冇食得飽嘅減肥餐單？","createTime":"2017-05-21T14:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T00:18:40.000Z","uid":81049,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f674b0a52397dd3e6271cbc2b8089b305c6fcf","tid":252301,"uid":81049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"男朋友以前好fit好大隻<br />\n又跑步又打籃球咁<br />\n之前整親之後差唔多冇做運動成年<br />\n但又冇減少食量 <br />\n依家變左個死肥仔<br />\n佢食2個m記餐都仲食得落<br />\n雖然做返運動 但都係好似冇乜成效<br />\n所以想請教下有冇食得飽嘅減肥餐<br />\n我都想佢快d變瘦 佢肥左之後成個人好懶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff436340f3ed98ebeead40601784913ac9f9f92","tid":252301,"uid":81049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"應承左整減肥餐比佢食 <br />\n但根本唔知咩係減肥餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b8c0bfad1a7fc1e98db3213a3d54919793550","tid":252301,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39aef301805d877c0089c3f06a9f126f18cb8403","tid":252301,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐麥皮<br />\n午餐麥皮<br />\n晚餐麥皮<br />\n最好唔好落糖</blockquote><br />\n奶都唔好落, 用熱水"},{"pid":"a1bced6a2c90f6aefeafa8ffbe44ba1accbf7bfa","tid":252301,"uid":89350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早餐麥皮<br />\n午餐麥皮<br />\n晚餐麥皮<br />\n最好唔好落糖</blockquote><br />\n奶都唔好落, 用熱水</blockquote><br />\n我早餐真係咁食<br />\n不過開大好促瀉瀉地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9af91f72819a8fc19083187fa7bdd42d02803c","tid":252301,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"每日出火三次<br />\n<br />\n唔做都吹爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr